  "original_title": "\u0dad\u0db1\u0dad\u0dd4\u0dbb\u0dd4 \u0db4\u0dc4\u0d9a\u0da7 \u0d8b\u0dc3\u0dc3\u0dca \u0db1\u0dd2\u0dbd\u0dad\u0dbd \u0d9a\u0db8\u0dd2\u0da7\u0dd4\u0dc0\u0dda \u0d85\u0db1\u0dd4\u0db8\u0dd0\u0dad\u0dd2\u0dba",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Approval of High Ranks Committee for five posts",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The approval of the Parliamentary Committee on High Officials to appoint an ambassador and five secretaries was received today (15).",
        "Accordingly, the approval of the Parliamentary Committee on High Officials of the Parliament has been given to appoint Mr. Admiral (Professor) Jayanath Colombo as the new Ambassador of Sri Lanka to the Republic of Indonesia.",
        "Meanwhile, as the secretary of the Ministry of Agriculture, M.B.R. Pushpakumara, RMCM as the Secretary of the Ministry of Wildlife and Forest Conservation. Herat and KMM as Secretary in the Ministry of Finance, Economic Stability and National Policy. Siriwardena, SJS Chandragupta as the new Secretary of the Ministry of Health and RPA as the Secretary of the Ministry of Labor and Foreign Employment. Parliamentary Secretary General Dhammika Dasanayake said that the Committee on Higher Positions also approved the appointment of Mr. Wimalaweera.",
        "Ministers (Dr.) Bandula Gunawardena, Douglas Devananda, Honorable Vidura Wickramanayake, Nimal Siripala de Silva, Ramesh Pathirana and Members of Parliament Thalatha Athukorala, Dr. Sudarshani Fernandopalle, and John Senaviratne participated in this meeting which was chaired by Speaker Mahinda Yapa Abeywardena."
      ],
